This is a placeholder. The license for agile_cards has not been chosen
yet. Candidates under consideration:

- MIT. Short, permissive, low friction. Fine for a portfolio piece.
- Apache-2.0. Permissive plus an explicit patent grant and a NOTICE
  mechanism. Better if this evolves into a product with patent surface.

No external contributions should be accepted until this file is replaced
with the real license text.

